PUNCTURE_WEAPON
CRAFTABLE
ENCRUSTABLE
SUBSTANCE HARDMETAL
IFPREVERB PULL -1
  IFITEM -1 WIELDED
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You raise %a in salute.
